</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_83" id="40r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Sweinfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als uns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        weisheit <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und an uns begert hat,
                        daz wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add>guten</add>
<expan>freunde<ex>n</ex></expan>, den von <expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan>,
                        Winsheim und <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>,
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sie <add>ir freunde</add> einen oder
                        czwen tag vor dem lantfrid, der yeczund schierst hie sein wirdt, czu uns her
                                    <add><expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan></add> wöllen, <add>darczu
                            ir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> freunde auch schicken wolt etc.</add>
                        Also lassen wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> ersamkeit wissen, daz wir
                            <add>das also</add> den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>freunde<ex>n</ex></expan>, <add><expan>v<ex>er</ex>kundet</expan> und
                            in</add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan>, <add>daz sie ir freunde her czu uns
                                    <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz die hie sein auf den <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>nehstkunftige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>freyt<ex>ag</ex></expan></q> 13.07.1408</note>
</app> czu nacht, ob ez sie <add><expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan></add>
                            auch gut dünke</add>, da wisz sich <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> nach czurihten.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
